      "type": "description",
      "value": {
        "latex": "On pose $f_0(t) = 0$, $f_{n+1}(t) = \\sqrt{t+f_n(t)}$, pour $t \\ge 0$.",
        "html": "<p>On pose <span class=\"math inline\">\\(f_0(t) = 0\\)</span>, <span class=\"math inline\">\\(f_{n+1}(t) = \\sqrt{t+f_n(t)}\\)</span>, pour <span class=\"math inline\">\\(t \\ge 0\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "cd9d9bea-898f-4400-9c1e-415e9d70cf11",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Déterminer la limite simple, $\\ell$, des fonctions $f_n$.",
        "html": "<p>Déterminer la limite simple, <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\ell\\)</span>, des fonctions <span class=\"math inline\">\\(f_n\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "0362274d-0860-4ad5-bc3c-d33faeab4f13",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Y a-t-il convergence uniforme sur $\\R^+$ ?",
        "html": "<p>Y a-t-il convergence uniforme sur <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\R^+\\)</span> ?</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "19a1b70c-5f44-4ab5-8a7b-a26613121b53",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Démontrer que : $\\forall\\ t > 0,\\\n    |f_{n+1}(t) - \\ell(t)| \\le \\frac {|f_n(t) - \\ell(t)|}{2f_{n+1}(t)}$.",
        "html": "<p>Démontrer que : <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\forall\\ t &gt; 0,\\\n    |f_{n+1}(t) - \\ell(t)| \\le \\frac {|f_n(t) - \\ell(t)|}{2f_{n+1}(t)}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "3be90a7f-ab22-4562-8e23-0d53d2106304",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "En déduire que la suite $(f_n)$ converge uniformément sur tout intervalle\n    $[a,+\\infty[$, avec $a>0$.\n    (Remarquer que $f_n - \\ell$ est bornée pour $n \\ge 1$)",
        "html": "<p>En déduire que la suite <span class=\"math inline\">\\((f_n)\\)</span> converge uniformément sur tout intervalle <span class=\"math inline\">\\([a,+\\infty[\\)</span>, avec <span class=\"math inline\">\\(a&gt;0\\)</span>. (Remarquer que <span class=\"math inline\">\\(f_n - \\ell\\)</span> est bornée pour <span class=\"math inline\">\\(n \\ge 1\\)</span>)</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "23ae7754-d85e-49bf-8fec-ea6ac7e83b28",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$\\ell(t) = \\begin{cases} 0 \\text{ si } t=0 \\cr\n                       \\frac {1+\\sqrt{1+4t}}2 \\text{ si } t >0.\\cr\\end{cases}$\nAccroissements finis.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\ell(t) = \\begin{cases} 0 \\text{ si } t=0 \\cr\n                       \\frac {1+\\sqrt{1+4t}}2 \\text{ si } t &gt;0.\\cr\\end{cases}\\)</span> Accroissements finis.</p>\n"
      }
    }
  ]
